title: Ep. - 255 - DIRECTOR OF DUDE PERFECT: BACKSTAGE PASS 25 YEARS AFTER REAL WORLD
description:
Shane Nickerson is Director of Dude Perfect: Backstage Pass, a YouTube Original documentary, a massively popular channel in which five friends orchestrate unfathomable sports trick shots.

 

Joe Patane appeared on Real World: Miami almost 25 years ago. He explains how the iconic show changed his life, the reality of filming, and how his time on the show and his work today has come full circle.

 

 

Reality Life with Kate Casey
